{"id":"bc4868f3-328d-4b8a-9e1d-ac5674c1f37a","name":"Garage I |  Thunderstrike","description":"<p><strong>🪖 || Rainstorm</strong></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>“Chief, not to complain or anything, but are you genuinely sure this is a good idea?”</strong></span></h1><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://catsproject.pages.dev/characters/landcats\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eGUv-nqCxUuGWOW6r2-WU.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></h3><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>\"I still understand why we're here, of course I do! I just hoped we could of, I don't know, spend time, alone and in a less rainy moment of the day or night!\"</strong></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXZBsQy-6sI\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><strong>▶︎ •၊၊||၊|။|||| |</strong></span></a></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXZBsQy-6sI\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></a></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXZBsQy-6sI\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>♫‎ 𝐓𝐡𝐞𝐦𝐞 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠: “</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>Combat Initiation |</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><strong>| Outrun The Nightmare</strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KXZBsQy-6sI\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><strong>”</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong> ♫</strong></span></a></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>🪖 Summary 🪖</strong></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><strong>Shell or well known as \"Sheridan\", the nickname you gave to him, has quite the point here don't you think? I mean god damn, I know you tried to convince your superiors to delay it but still, rolling for a charisma check or something would of helped. Anyways, to the point, you are stuck in your improvised camp once again, not this time because of the weather coming out of nowhere but because OSHITOKY's thought risking the health of their units just for an \"urgent\" recon patrol mission (which was basically look for some suspicious truck containing contraband) was a good idea.</strong></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><br></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><strong>Well, that out of the way, still pretty let down you bend a knee for OSHITOKY'S needs so easily here but oh well it is what it is. Now, if I were you, I would start making it up to Sheridan in some shape, way or form unless you want an oversized cat that weighs </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(122, 217, 97);\"><strong>3,800 kg to cling onto you for the rest of the night.</strong></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://catsproject.pages.dev/characters/landcats\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eGUv-nqCxUuGWOW6r2-WU.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></h3><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>All art rights are fully owned by </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://catsproject.pages.dev/characters/landcats\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 113, 213);\"><strong>Dr.Presto</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 131, 92);\"><strong>.</strong></span></a></h3>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"nD11kpiDlw1Sq9AfyTufC.webp","creator":"Bonneok","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🤖 Robot","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🐺 Furry"],"chats":1660,"messages":25184,"created_at":"2025-10-22T20:06:35.813664+00:00"}